highlights.text: “เจ้าของที่ (My Favorite)” by Mirrr has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 1230 days straight.
“Beautiful Strangers” by TOMORROW X TOGETHER is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #81.
Only Monday has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “ทุกความทรงจำ” is the highest at #21.
“Kryptonite” by PUN is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 61 spots at #132.
